Careers
















Our employees
The key to our success 










We owe the success of our business to the women and men on our teams. Our employees' commitment is the foundation of the excellent service the Edmond de Rothschild Group guarantees its clients. We make sure that each one can advance in their career by providing an environment that promotes professional development. 
















Our culture, our values
Concordia, Integritas, Industria



Learn more


















Profiles sought 










We know that the world is changing quickly and we're looking for a range of profiles. Experience in finance is an asset.
Young graduatesTo provide the best for our clients, we recruit young employees from diverse backgrounds with degrees acknowledged for their excellence and who identify with our values. They are entrepreneurs who like teamwork, and are curious and committed. They form a talent pool which contributes to the Edmond de Rothschild Group's prestige.We attend many career forums and offer internships at different stages of students' education.Experienced candidates
Our business lines recruit people at different stages in their careers. Please contact us.














The recruiting process 










Our recruiting process is designed to match the skills and personality of each candidate with our needs and professional environment. It always includes meetings with selected business professionals and an HR representative.Would you like to join us? Our current offers are available in the "Employment Offers" section. Or, feel free to send us an unsolicited application.

















